sequenceDiagram
    participant UI as UIMain/UIGame
    participant WF as WorkFlow
    participant SDK as SDKAdapter
    participant App as SDKImpl(App/HLDDZ/Web)
    participant Share as ShareManager
    participant PM as PlayerManager

    UI->>WF: onShareBtnClick()
    WF->>SDK: HLDDZ_shareMessage / shareMessage2
    App-->>SDK: rspShareMessage(isSuccess)
    SDK-->>WF: 回调（成功: 动画/奖励；失败: 提示）
    Note over UI,WF: 新手引导分支会打 Guild 上报

    App-->>SDK: rspCpMiniGameByShare(extraStr)
    SDK->>PM: 保存 extraStr
    SDK->>Share: parseExtraStr() 解包/构建 ShareMapData
    Share->>UI: removeAllUI → emit uiGame({gameType: Share})

